{"tid":249483,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求答案 數學題","createTime":"2017-05-19T10:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T10:53:57.000Z","uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1dc636c2077211003462bfdb6deb37341a3bb2e","tid":249483,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:30:16.000Z","msg":"農場裡有100隻雞，安靜地圍成一個圈。忽然，每隻雞都把自己身旁的一隻雞啄了一下。如果每隻雞啄左邊或右邊是隨機的，會有多少隻雞沒有被啄？<br />\n<br />\n4自乘2017次，減3自乘2017次，餘數的個位數是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n若干個連續整數，最小的一個是 －32。如果全部這些整數加起來是67，共有多少個整數？ <br />\n<br />\n袋子裡有1分、5分和10分三種硬幣，每種最少有5個。任意從袋中取出5個硬幣，可以有多少個不同的總值？<br />\n<br />\n有一數，是2、3、4和5的倍數，同時又是一個2次、3次、4次和5次方。如果這數等如a的b次方， a + b最小是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%A5%B5%E9%80%9F%E8%A7%A3%E9%A1%8C-78630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%2580%259F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%25A1%258C-78630&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=43018b64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%A5%B5%E9%80%9F%E8%A7%A3%E9%A1%8C-78630</a>"},{"pid":"969aa5aacbaacd04c1d668323870fc3be4d44352","tid":249483,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"第一題係咪問最多幾多隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e27943f36c1c1714628527d1ec8d12dc6e3c61","tid":249483,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"曾鈺成個fb有人comment曬啲答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}